本模板用于舍入小数至若干位，或是將小數補零到所設定之小數位數。

==用法==
<code><nowiki>{{Rnd|數字|小數位數}}</nowiki></code>
*數字：填入數
*位數：設定之小數位數。

==示例==
*{{xpsoc|Rnd|2.0004|3}}
*{{xpsoc|Rnd|0.000020004|7}}
*{{xpsoc|Rnd|154268|-3}}
*{{xpsoc|Rnd|154268988|-6}}
*{{xpsoc|Rnd|1542689271|-7}}

*{{xpsoc|Rnd|1|2}}
*{{xpsoc|Rnd|1.2|2}}
*{{xpsoc|Rnd|1.23|2}}
*{{xpsoc|Rnd|1.234|2}}

*{{xpsoc|Rnd|-1|2}}
*{{xpsoc|Rnd|-1.2|2}}
*{{xpsoc|Rnd|-1.23|2}}
*{{xpsoc|Rnd|-1.234|2}}

